item.title: theming the T610
item.description:
i recently experienced a painless switch from sprint to t-mobile. It ruled. and part of the divorce i ended up with a sony ericcson t610. so as any good person would.. i went about creating some themes to make it look better than the defaults that came with it.

here they are. most of them are generic - but a couple are nice.
